Name: Del Cheeseburger
Description: A 100% beef patty grilled to order, American cheese, two fresh tomato slices, burger sauce, crisp shredded lettuce, and diced onions on a grilled sesame seed bun.

Name: Bean & Cheese Burrito
Description: Slow-cooked beans made from scratch, fresh house-grated cheddar cheese, and zesty red or tangy green sauce, wrapped in a warm flour tortilla.

Name: Cheddar Quesadilla
Description: Fresh house-grated cheddar cheese and tangy green sauce folded in a flour tortilla and flat-grilled to perfection.

Name: Queso Loaded Nachos
Description: Loaded with choice of seasoned beef, freshly grilled, marinated chicken, freshly grilled carne asada, or Beyond Meat®, fresh house-made tortilla chips, slow-cooked beans made from scratch, and signature creamy Queso Blanco, topped with cool sour cream, fresh diced tomatoes, and sliced jalapeños.

Name: Snack Taco
Description: Seasoned beef, crisp shredded lettuce, fresh house-grated cheddar cheese in a crunchy corn shell or warm flour tortilla.
